OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772967895
OL,3,CFarm machinery and vehicles worth
OL,4,Caround #200,000 recovered in police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FFarm machinery and vehicles worth
OL,8,Faround #200,000 have been recovered
OL,9,Ffollowing an operation led by Kent
OL,10,FPolice's Rural Task Force.
OL,12,FA woodchipper was recovered, along
OL,13,Fwith an excavator and trailer,
OL,14,Fdiagnostic equipment and a tool to
OL,15,Fchange VIN numbers.
OL,17,FThree arrests were made over a two-day
OL,18,Fperiod after the suspected stolen
OL,19,Fgoods were recovered in Dover.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
