OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772967895
OL,3,CFarm machinery and vehicles worth
OL,4,Caround #200,000 recovered in police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FOn Thursday 26 February 2026, drivers
OL,8,Fwho were attempting to leave the
OL,9,Fcountry, were stopped by officers
OL,10,Fafter there were suspicions that the
OL,11,Fmachinery they were travelling with
OL,12,Fwere stolen goods.
OL,14,FTwo men, aged 43 and 44, were arrested
OL,15,Fin connection with handling stolen
OL,16,Fgoods and going equipped. They have
OL,17,Fsince been bailed pending further
OL,18,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772967895
OL,3,CFarm machinery and vehicles worth
OL,4,Caround #200,000 recovered in police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe following day, a lorry was stopped
OL,8,Fafter it was suspected that the Volvo
OL,9,FG930 grader it was towing had been
OL,10,Fstolen. The value of the grader was
OL,11,Festimated at around #150,000.
OL,13,FA suspected stolen John Deere baler
OL,14,Fwas also seized.
OL,16,FEnquiries were completed at the scene
OL,17,Fand a 31-year-old man was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of handling stolen goods,
OL,19,Falong with two driving offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
