OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772967895
OL,3,CFarm machinery and vehicles worth
OL,4,Caround #200,000 recovered in police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FHe has been bailed while enquiries
OL,8,Fcontinue.
OL,10,FSgt Ross Haybourne said: "It shows
OL,11,Fwhat can be achieved when police
OL,12,Fofficers and specialist partners work
OL,13,Fclosely together.
OL,15,F"Through working collaboratively, we
OL,16,Fwere able to recover valuable
OL,17,Fagricultural and construction
OL,18,Fmachinery and safeguard farmers,
OL,19,Fbusinesses and livelihoods."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
